data.description: It's Cold Outside! Isn't it Time to settle in to YOUR new Home? This home will not disappoint. This 3 bedroom, 1 bathroom IMMACULATE home is ready for new owners. Cozy & Open concept Living rm, Dining area and Kitchen make for great get-togethers. Bedrooms all have well-kept and recently cleaned carpets. Full bathroom with washer/dryer included and Wonderful warm color palette throughout! The attached carport with a side door access into the kitchen/dining area will make you smile! The carport is big enough to put 2 cars in behind each other OR 1 car in & make the rest a great patio area! Or maybe you really want some extra storage space or a workshop....well look no further! There is a sizeable barn with gravel base in the back. So Many Possibilities! Come Home & Come Enjoy this Peaceful setting that is The Station in the heart of Brandenburg. Minutes from Nucor, shopping, dining, parks and recreation. WELCOME TO MEADE COUNTY!
